titles.title: Recognizing the historic significance of the 30th anniversary of the founding of the Department of Defense State Partnership Program.
Recognizing the historic significance of the 30th anniversary of the founding of the Department of Defense State Partnership Program.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Armed Services.

bill.summary: This resolution recognizes the 30th anniversary of the founding of the Department of Defense State Partnership Program and its outsized influence in developing and supporting enduring relationships around the world. The resolution also expresses deep gratitude for the service of members of the National Guard to the program.
